<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hurghada</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
        .image-end-1{
            position: relative;
            cursor: pointer;
            height: 340px;
            width: 380px;
            margin: 40px;
            box-shadow: 10px 10px 5px #aaaaaa;
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-image: url("https://media.kempinski.com/34368006/sunrise-1.jpg;width=1905;height=794;mode=crop;anchor=middlecenter;autorotate=true;quality=85;scale=both;progressive=true;encoder=freeimage;format=jpg");
        }
        .dark{
            background-color: #333;
        }
        .image-end-1-big{
            z-index: 111;
            position: absolute;
            cursor: pointer;
            height: 540px;
            width: 880px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-left: 400px;
            background-size: cover;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-image: url("https://media.kempinski.com/34368006/sunrise-1.jpg;width=1905;height=794;mode=crop;anchor=middlecenter;autorotate=true;quality=85;scale=both;progressive=true;encoder=freeimage;format=jpg");
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 15px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: rgb(37, 37, 37); 
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: #333; 
            border-radius: 25px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: #555; 
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/hurghada/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div id="image-1-big" class="image-end-1-big invisible"></div>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Hurghada</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Hurghada este una dintre cele mai importante stațiuni din Egipt, aflate pe coasta de est. Și da, este și cea mai veche și renumită stațiune din Deșertul Estic al Egiptului. La bază, zona are un trecut pescăresc care a migrat treptat către un univers al vacanțelor all-inclusive, dominat de o linie generoasă de plaje și un număr mare de hoteluri dispuse de-a lungul coastei. Acestea au diferite grade de accesibilitate și confort, de la hoteluri de cinci stele, până la pensiuni.    
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        Hurghada is one of the most important resorts in Egypt, located on the east coast. And yes, it is also the oldest and most famous resort in the Eastern Desert of Egypt. Basically, the area has a fishing past that has gradually migrated to a universe of all-inclusive holidays, dominated by a generous line of beaches and a large number of hotels arranged along the coast. They have varying degrees of accessibility and comfort, from five-star hotels to guesthouses.
    </p>
    <div class="images-section" id="images-section">
        <div id="image-1" class="image-end-1"></div>
    </div>
</body>
<script>
    const image1 = document.getElementById("image-1")
    const imageBig1 = document.getElementById("image-1-big")
    const body = document.querySelector("body")

    image1.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        imageBig1.classList.remove("invisible")
        body.classList.add("dark")
        image1.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    imageBig1.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        imageBig1.classList.add("invisible")
        body.classList.remove("dark")
        image1.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>